Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Glan Vocational High School in the Municipality of Glan, Province of South Cotabato, to Glan School of Arts and Trades
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 781
An Act Changing the Name of the Glan Vocational High School in the Municipality of Glan, Province of South Cotabato, to Glan School of Arts and Trades
Section 1. The name of the Glan Vocational High School in the Municipality of Glan, Province of South Cotabato, is changed to Glan School of Arts and Trades.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
